cs.SY, cs.DC, cs.AI, cs.ET, cs.SE 

The paper deals with the modeling and control of distributed battery storage in low voltage grids, which involves optimization and control algorithms. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves power systems and electrical engineering, which could fall under cs.ET (Emerging Technologies) and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
